<td bgcolor="#EEEEEE" colspan=2 class=news>
<table><tr><td valign=top><img src='images/icon_general.gif' alt='General News' border=0></td><td width="100%" valign=top><IMG SRC="http://www.codemasters.com/flashpoint/gold/images/goldup_pack.jpg" align=right> Codemaster’s send <A HREF="http://www.codemasters.com/flashpoint/gold/front.htm" target=_new>word</A> that they are to release a gold edition of the popular war game, Operation Flashpoint.<br><br>Due for release in the UK on the 30th of November at £34.99, the gold edition will include the original Op. Flashpoint game patched to V1.3, all addition vehicles, weapons and missions contained in those patches and Red Hammer : The Soviet Campaign. Red Hammer is a brand new campaign featuring 20 new missions and Russian accents :) Also, just in case you get stuck, Codemasters are going to be very generous and bung in the official Prima Strategy Guide.<br><br>As well as the full gold edition, an upgrade pack will also be released for a very reasonably priced £9.99. This will include Red Hammer, all 3 patches and the strategy guide. The upgrade will also be available to download for £4.99 but will only include Red Hammer and the strategy guide in PDF format.<br><br>[ Taken from <A HREF="http://www.barrysworld.com/news/" target_new>BarrysWorld</A> ]</td></tr></table>
