<td bgcolor="#CECECE" class="btext" width="100%"><b>Ghost Recon Goes Gold</b> - <span class=bsmall>posted by  <a class='nNewsMailLink' href='mailto:StealthBuda@barrysworld.com'>StealthBuda</a> on Wed 24 October 2001 02:31:30 | <a href="comments.php?section=1&index=444" class=blink>Comments (0)</a></span></td>
