<td bgcolor="#CECECE" class="btext" width="100%"><b>Max Payne Cinematics</b> - <span class=bsmall>posted by  <a class='nNewsMailLink' href='mailto:StealthBuda@barrysworld.com'>StealthBuda</a> on Tue 23 October 2001 06:52:56 | <a href="comments.php?section=1&index=439" class=blink>Comments (0)</a></span></td>
